    <PrimAttribute name="onlyBookingRefWith" id="0e683721-47d3-41c3-b5c8-1c4c87a9c44c">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Integer"/>
        <text>
MES1008

This is to handle queries where they only want to inlcude if the Tracked Item does not have a bookingRef, or if it does have a bookingRef.
Set this Integer using the class constants

Only_State_All			0			Default value. Will include any transaction regardless of booking ref value
OnlyState_NullValue		1           Will only include transaction that have a null booking ref
OnlyState_WithValue		2			Will only include transaction that have a  booking ref value, excludes null values</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
    <PrimAttribute name="onlyConsigneeWith" id="736e0adf-3a92-4392-adcf-5c32ebfb845c">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Integer"/>
        <text>
MES1008

This is to handle queries where they only want to inlcude if it does not have a Consignee, or if it does have a Consignee value.
Set this Integer using the class constants

Only_State_All			0			Default value. Will include any transaction regardless of Consignee value
OnlyState_NullValue		1           Will only include transaction that have a null Consignee
OnlyState_WithValue		2			Will only include transaction that have a  Consignee value, excludes null values</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
